BEYOND the DARKNESS goes WAY BEYOND today as we decipher Transmissions From the Solar Council with Marc Brinkerhoff.

A true "UFO Repeater" who has established contact with humanoid-like entities from other spheres and dimensions. He has the ability to aim his camera at the sky where they "tell him" and
unexplained images will appear (including the shadow of an alien in one case).

Marc is in touch with the Ashtar Command who have promised to assist in a global evacuation if there is any sort of widespread disaster. He is the principal individual who tells his experience in "Ashtar's Space Brothers Speak -- Transmissions From The Solar Council." And his on going experiences are related in "UFO Repeaters -- The Camera Doesn't Lie!"
